
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "AboutUs";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/MasterPage.cshtml";
}
<link rel="stylesheet" href="~/CSS/AboutUsCSS.css" />
<div class="main-container">
    <h1 class="page-title">frequently asked questions</h1>

    <!-- FAQ Grid -->
    <div class="faq-section">
        <div class="faq-grid">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3 class="faq-question">How can I find the cheapest flight using SkyPath?</h3>
                <p class="faq-answer">
                    Find the cheapest time to fly. If you have a destination in mind and want to find the cheapest flight, simply select the <strong>'sort by price: low to high'</strong> option during your search. This will help you find the cheapest day to fly.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3 class="faq-question">How does SkyPath work?</h3>
                <p class="faq-answer">
                    We're a flight search engine. We scan all the top airlines and travel providers across the web, so you can compare airlines and other travel related costs – all in one place. Once you've found the best flight, you can book directly with the provider.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3 class="faq-question">What happens after I book my flight?</h3>
                <p class="faq-answer">
                    Your flight booking confirmation email and any additional information you need will come from the airline or supplier you booked with. If you have any further questions about your booking, or if you want to change or cancel your flight, please contact them.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3 class="faq-question">Where should I book a flight to now?</h3>
                <p class="faq-answer">
                    If you're looking for inspiration for your next trip, it's worth <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=travel+destinations&oq=travel+destinatio&gs_lcrp=EgZjaHJvbWUqBwgCEAAYgAQyBwgAEAAYgAQyBggBEEUYOTIHCAIQABiABDIHCAMQABiABDIHCAQQABiABDIHCAUQABiABDIHCAYQABiABDIHCAcQABiABDIHCAgQABiABDIHCAkQABiABNIBCTE3MzAzajBqN6gCALACAA&sourceid=chrome&ie=UTF-8">searching the world</a> to find a cheap flight ticket to anywhere.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3 class="faq-question">Is it possible to book a flexible flight ticket?</h3>
                <p class="faq-answer">
                    We understand how important it is to keep your vacation plans flexible. Sometimes, there may be an additional fee for a changeable flight ticket, so it's a good idea to look for this option when booking. You can also use our free cancellations, so you can book at the moment and change or even cancel it later if necessary.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3 class="faq-question">Should I book my flight through SkyPath?</h3>
                <p class="faq-answer">
                    We are a search engine, so once you find the best flight ticket, you can book it directly through the airline or travel provider's website. This way, you will have the opportunity to add any details you want about the customer, e.g. ordering a spefic program, and you can choose your preferred flight options, such as seats on the plane.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

