    <!-- Child Safety Policy -->
    <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-title">Child Safety Policy</h2>
        <div class="policy-content">
            <p>
                At our site, the safety and well-being of children are our top priority. We are committed to creating a secure and respectful online environment. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13 without parental consent. Any content on our site is designed to be safe, inclusive, and appropriate for all users.
            </p>
            <p>
                If you believe a child has provided us with personal information without parental consent, please contact us immediately, and we will promptly remove the information.
            </p>
            <p>
                Your trust means everything to us, and we are dedicated to ensuring a safe and positive experience for all families who use our website.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Accessibility Statement -->
    <div class="policy-section">
        <h2 class="policy-title">Accessibility Statement</h2>
        <div class="policy-content">
            <p>
                At our site, we are committed to making our website accessible to everyone, including people with disabilities. Our goal is to provide an inclusive and user-friendly experience for all visitors.
            </p>
            <p>
                We strive to follow recognized accessibility standards, such as the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG), and continuously work to improve our site's design and functionality.
